- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning techniques applied to natural language processing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of convolutional neural networks, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possibility as the paper discusses the use of neural networks for the classification tasks.
